    "body": "It is pretty simple to do this via GraphQL if that's an option for you. You can get multiple blocks, their txes and receipt fields (logs) all in one request. I can help you write a query if you describe the data fields you need. Also see https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interacting-with-geth/rpc/graphql.\r\n\r\nOtherwise there's a PR for this: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/25316 but the requirement is this method needs to be specc'ed and agreen on by other clients before we add it.",
